    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained over the years. The exterior is clean and presents well, though you will find some minor signs of normal wear such as small stone chips on the hood and light surface scratches consistent with its age. Inside, the cabin is tidy and the upholstery is in great shape with no major tears or stains. Mechanically, the car is sound; the engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts as it should. It is a reliable choice for anyone looking for a dependable vehicle that has been cared for properly.",
