      "description": "Available is a mechanically sorted E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six engine. This power plant utilizes individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system to deliver exceptional throttle response across the rev range. Power is managed through a tactile 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and sent to the rear wheels via a variable M-Differential lock. This example has undergone critical preventative maintenance, including subframe reinforcement and a top-end VANOS overhaul to ensure long-term structural and timing integrity. The chassis remains taut with a MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension setup. While displaying minor aesthetic wear consistent with its 'good' status, the vehicle\u2019s performance envelope remains fully intact for the discerning enthusiast.",
